tags.description: More an abandoned small bunker, than a shelter. It lies underground, is build out of concrete and is encased with natural stones. 2 entrances, no doors left (stairs and a ramp on the other side). Unfortunately it is misused as a latrine and stinks!
Tunnels under the rock, reachable from the south via swimming.
